, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 293.96174643705467, 558.8036773109243, 9.62303355106883], "text": "\u201cSales finance is a core business in the auto world. Automotive financing supports car", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3221, "box": [292.99289075630253, 293.96174643705467, 583.9381243697478, 60.75263865795728], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 311.0049521971497, 583.9381243697478, 9.62303355106883], "text": "sales and provides additional income, which translates into increased profit for the Group.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3221, "box": [292.99289075630253, 293.96174643705467, 583.9381243697478, 60.75263865795728], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 328.048145783848, 572.3190172268908, 9.62303355106883], "text": "All Nissan finance companies operate under strict risk management control policies and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3221, "box": [292.99289075630253, 293.96174643705467, 583.9381243697478, 60.75263865795728], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 345.091351543943, 376.98039159663864, 9.623033551068943], "text": "must balance the drive for profit with active sales support.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 362.134557304038, 526.5571256302521, 9.623021377672217], "text": "In Japan, about fifty percent of customers use cash when buying a car. Corporate", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 8, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 379.1777508907363, 538.6052340336134, 9.623033551068943], "text": "sales account for another 20 percent of the total, while the remaining 30 percent of", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 396.2208836104513, 560.7160000000001, 9.623106591448959], "text": "customers use automotive financing. Therefore, we focus on capturing that 30 percent", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 413.2640771971496, 577.479142857143, 9.623070071259008], "text": "market, in addition to penetrating the cash customer segment. Nissan Financial Services,", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 430.3072464370546, 521.4716613445378, 9.623070071259008], "text": "or NFS, has the highest level of market penetration in Japan, and our centralized", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3222, "box": [292.99289075630253, 362.134557304038, 577.479142857143, 94.8389162707839], "id_box_line": 12, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 447.3504035035629, 483.46903697478996, 9.623070071259008], "text": "customer center gives us a clear advantage over other finance companies.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEHF+NissanAG-Medium", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 573.0028214285715, 12.106455166270848], "text": "A sales finance company is exposed to various forms of risk. One risk is interest rate fluctuation.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 498.47890083135394, 571.9866071428571, 12.106455166270734], "text": "NFS mitigates this risk by matching interest as much as possible. Almost seventy percent of our", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 515.5220578978622, 538.6038214285713, 12.106455166270848], "text": "portfolio is on a match-funding basis. Another risk is credit risk. Fortunately, our portfolio is", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 532.5652271377672, 575.9562857142857, 12.106455166270791], "text": "improving. The economy is getting better, and we\u2019ve had success with a low-interest, 2.9 percent", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 549.6083842042756, 551.4675886554621, 12.106455166270734], "text": "APR program. Because this is a competitive rate, it has attracted customers with good credit", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3223, "box": [292.99289075630253, 481.43573159144887, 575.9562857142857, 97.32227701900246], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 566.6515534441805, 359.39278697479, 12.106455166270791], "text": "ratings who otherwise would have opted for bank financing. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 583.6947226840855, 543.1811268907563, 12.106442992874065], "text": "We have also improved our scoring system for credit analysis. We have a new system that", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 600.7378797505938, 563.3912327731093, 12.106455166270791], "text": "can automatically process 60 percent of all credit applications. Turnaround time for the credit", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 617.7810489904989, 552.0928214285716, 12.106442992874065], "text": "decision used to take three to four hours, but with continuous improvement of our system it", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 634.8242060570071, 539.2510357142858, 12.106455166270734], "text": "takes just 14 minutes. If the dealer submits the data online, turnaround is reduced to four", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 651.8673752969121, 580.0065, 12.106455166270734], "text": "minutes. This has really increased customer satisfaction. In addition, having a centralized system", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3224, "box": [292.99289075630253, 583.6947226840855, 580.0065, 97.32226484560567], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 668.9105323634204, 350.0829273109244, 12.106455166270791], "text": "ensures that our credit standards are consistently applied.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3225, "box": [292.99289075630253, 685.9537016033254, 584.1812130252101, 46.19278147268409], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 685.9537016033254, 557.4476626050421, 12.106455166270848], "text": "The above improvements have reduced our loss ratio to below 0.3 percent. More importantly, 95", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3225, "box": [292.99289075630253, 685.9537016033254, 584.1812130252101, 46.19278147268409], "id_box_line": 26, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 702.9968708432305, 582.3683756302521, 12.106430819477396], "text": "percent of applicants are approved for financing. The challenge is to reduce the loss ratio and rejection", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3225, "box": [292.99289075630253, 685.9537016033254, 584.1812130252101, 46.19278147268409], "id_box_line": 27, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 720.0400522565321, 584.1812130252101, 12.106430819477396], "text": "rate at the same time. We want to support sales by providing financing, and keep the loss ratio low. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3226, "box": [292.99289075630253, 737.0832336698338, 585.4067857142859, 63.23597505938241], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 737.0832336698338, 532.0995159663864, 12.106430819477453], "text": "In the past, NFS depended on the parent company for funding. Since Nissan and NFS had", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3226, "box": [292.99289075630253, 737.0832336698338, 585.4067857142859, 63.23597505938241], "id_box_line": 29, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 754.1264150831354, 574.6018042016806, 12.106430819477453], "text": "their financial ratings upgraded, we issued our first public bond in September 2003. We have also", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3226, "box": [292.99289075630253, 737.0832336698338, 585.4067857142859, 63.23597505938241], "id_box_line": 30, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 771.1695964964371, 585.4067857142859, 12.106430819477453], "text": "issued commercial paper and diversified our funding sources. As a result, our reliance on the parent", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3226, "box": [292.99289075630253, 737.0832336698338, 585.4067857142859, 63.23597505938241], "id_box_line": 31, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 788.2127779097387, 324.8795554621849, 12.106430819477453], "text": "company for funding has been reduced to almost zero. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 32, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 805.2559593230404, 550.2214987394957, 12.106430819477424], "text": "Sales finance became actively involved in sales support during NISSAN 180. We have always", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 33, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 822.299140736342, 560.6925542016807, 12.106430819477424], "text": "been a source of profit, but now we are aiming to enhance the value chain as well. We have the", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 34, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 839.3423221496437, 555.0404457983193, 12.106442992874094], "text": "largest number of business lines of any finance company, including credit loans, corporate and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 35, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 856.3855035629454, 581.1178756302522, 12.106442992874094], "text": "private leasing, car rentals, credit cards, insurance, maintenance and much more. Because we have", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 36, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 873.428684976247, 570.4359285714286, 12.106442992874094], "text": "more touch points with the customer, we have a great opportunity to easily cross-sell our products.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 37, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 890.4718663895487, 574.615, 12.106442992874108], "text": "Nissan is allocating more resources to light commercial vehicles, which is a perfect platform for us", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 38, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 907.5150478028504, 577.8159285714287, 12.106442992874108], "text": "as well. And two years ago we created a fleet division with Nissan that provides both vehicles and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3227, "box": [292.99289075630253, 805.2559593230404, 581.1178756302522, 131.40871288598572], "id_box_line": 39, "box_line": [292.99289075630253, 924.5582304334916, 428.454392857143, 12.106441775534435], "text": "a full range of services including total outsourcing of fleet management.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3228, "box": [317.4083735294118, 941.601413064133, 558.0026268907563, 12.106441775534435], "id_box_line": 40, "box_line": [317.4083735294118, 941.601413064133, 558.0026268907563, 12.106441775534435], "text": "The Alliance with Renault has played a central role in our development over the past few years.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEIG+NissanAG-Light", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3229, "box": [50.94542857142857, 991.5326556116389, 170.10365966386559, 10.18913179928741], "id_box_line": 0, "box_line": [78.13394289915966, 992.6264340855107, 142.91514533613451, 7.924881235154388], "text": "Nissan Annual Report 2004", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEGB+NissanAG-Regular", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3229, "box": [50.94542857142857, 991.5326556116389, 170.10365966386559, 10.18913179928741], "id_box_line": 1, "box_line": [50.94542857142857, 991.5326556116389, 17.408114201680682, 10.18913179928741], "text": "28", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEGC+NissanAG-Bold", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3230, "box": [12.245963722689076, 465.61563568883616, 9.612497201680675, 61.30279097387165], "id_box_line": 44, "box_line": [12.245963722689076, 465.61563568883616, 2.403083731092437, 61.30279097387165], "text": "WHO", "category": "Page-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/MENEGB+NissanAG-Regular", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 3230, "box": [12.245963722689076, 465.61563568883616, 9.612497201680675, 61.30279097387165], "id_box_line": 45, "box_line": [18.494119789915967, 465.61563568883616, 0.8410443697478982, 61.30279097387165], "text": "WE", "category": "Page-header"